{"tid":1199513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警懷疑水樽是武器　驅逐《立場》記者　搜查背包阻採訪","createTime":"2019-06-10T13:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T17:26:01.000Z","uid":52490,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff99c7f8bb090cc9a10756016a7b14e48cf9203","tid":1199513,"uid":52490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:37:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2237174903034784?s=100003289508463&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmwa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2237174903034784%3Fs%3D100003289508463%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dxmwa&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=8d065e0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2237174903034784?s=100003289508463&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmwa</a><br />\n<br />\n【7 分鐘影片全紀錄】 警懷疑水樽是武器　驅逐《立場》記者　搜查背包阻採訪<br />\n<br />\n昨日（6 月 9 日）反送中遊行結束後，有示威群眾今日（10 日）凌晨試圖衝擊立法會，引發警民衝突。警方在擴大封鎖範圍期間，有警員以懷疑記者藏有攻擊性武器為理由，搜尋《立場新聞》記者背包，並懷疑記者背包內為同事補給的樽裝食水是攻擊性武器。《立場新聞》譴責警方無理阻礙記者正常採訪工作，香港記者協會亦發聲明抗議，斥警方之行為踐踏採訪權，促請警方嚴查事件，提供合理解釋。<br />\n<br />\n記者採訪手記<br />\n警員懷疑我藏有攻擊性武器　「點解有咁多水？係咪要黎掟我哋？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2R124bl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2R124bl&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=c663889b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2R124bl</a><br />\n<br />\n稱懷疑水樽是武器　警惡意驅逐《立場》記者　搜查背包阻採訪<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2I8rWze\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2I8rWze&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=47d9d8be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2I8rWze</a><br />\n<br />\n記協斥踐踏採訪權　警：有示威者出示偽造記者證　搜袋或因要核證身份<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2EVImJ9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2EVImJ9&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=d8181aa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2EVImJ9</a><br />\n<br />\n警方連番阻礙記者採訪　記協斥嚴重踐踏採訪權<